### 事项详情管理接口

@baseUrl = http://localhost

### 分页查询事项详情
POST {{baseUrl}}/console/issue-detail/page
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "current": 1,
  "size": 10,
  "companyId": null,
  "companyCode": "",
  "companyName": "",
  "templateFieldId": null,
  "valueString": "",
  "valueJson": ""
}

### 获取事项详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/console/issue-detail/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 创建事项详情
POST {{baseUrl}}/console/issue-detail
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "companyId": 1,
  "companyCode": "COMP001",
  "companyName": "示例公司",
  "templateFieldId": 1,
  "valueString": "示例值",
  "valueJson": "{\"key\": \"value\"}"
}

### 更新事项详情
PUT {{baseUrl}}/console/issue-detail/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "companyId": 1,
  "companyCode": "COMP001",
  "companyName": "示例公司",
  "templateFieldId": 1,
  "valueString": "更新后的值",
  "valueJson": "{\"updated\": true, \"value\": \"new value\"}"
}

### 删除事项详情
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/console/issue-detail/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 根据企业ID查询事项详情列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/console/issue-detail/company/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 根据模板字段ID查询事项详情列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/console/issue-detail/template-field/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 查询特定企业的分页事项详情
POST {{baseUrl}}/console/issue-detail/page
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "current": 1,
  "size": 10,
  "companyId": 1
}

### 查询特定模板字段的分页事项详情
POST {{baseUrl}}/console/issue-detail/page
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "current": 1,
  "size": 10,
  "templateFieldId": 1
}

### 根据字符串值模糊查询事项详情
POST {{baseUrl}}/console/issue-detail/page
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "current": 1,
  "size": 10,
  "valueString": "示例"
}

### 根据JSON值模糊查询事项详情
POST {{baseUrl}}/console/issue-detail/page
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "current": 1,
  "size": 10,
  "valueJson": "value"
}












